  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minigames Mayhem is a fun collection of party minigames in which you can spend countless hours solo or with friends. Some people like cars, some like to complete impossible challenges and some want only relaxing games to chill. Minigames Mayhem offers these things and much more.  Run, jump, race, and compete in a collection of games designed to be replayed and mastered. Each game has a way to compete even with friends on a couch or across a distance online. Even though we like fair play and in an even environment... You will probably find some things a bit overpowered and unfair - take it to your advantage or get demolished by others! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Mile High Jump</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/be279bfcc782aeaec2521526330ba610.webp?t=1748186612\" width=592 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever thought about the definition of insanity? Well, you will test your limits in the Mile high jump. Each map of this minigame offers a unique challenge to reach the top while getting through difficult obstacles and jumps. Some maps can take you a couple of hours, and some… Some will take up to days to beat and reach the top. Will you take on a challenge and get your record on the leaderboard? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5/5 difficulty</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hard mode available</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards available</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/c2ba9ef87927315273f6090e01900d37.poster.avif?t=1748186612\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/c2ba9ef87927315273f6090e01900d37.webm?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/c2ba9ef87927315273f6090e01900d37.mp4?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demolition derby</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/be279bfcc782aeaec2521526330ba610.webp?t=1748186612\" width=592 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smashing cars, upgrading them, and destroying everyone in the way is always fun… With that in mind, we have created a Demolition derby minigame where you can play against 3 other opponents. Each round, you will be upgrading your vehicle into the ultimate demolition machine, and after the dust settles in, only one can be crowned the “Demolition champion”.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3/5 difficulty</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards available</strong><br></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/73a93c3e5808e2938dcdc2a393584923.poster.avif?t=1748186612\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/73a93c3e5808e2938dcdc2a393584923.webm?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/73a93c3e5808e2938dcdc2a393584923.mp4?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ultra racing simulator</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/be279bfcc782aeaec2521526330ba610.webp?t=1748186612\" width=592 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may not be about demolition and more about actual speed and racing. Well, this is a minigame for you. On unique maps, you can compete to win the race while picking up power-ups and trying to distract your rivals. Some maps have unique obstacles you must overcome, so start your engine, and let´s go!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2/5 difficulty</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards available</strong><br><strong></strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/008b719d7c943b559d8a1c4e9c1e1b3a.poster.avif?t=1748186612\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/008b719d7c943b559d8a1c4e9c1e1b3a.webm?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/008b719d7c943b559d8a1c4e9c1e1b3a.mp4?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Zombie Friday</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/be279bfcc782aeaec2521526330ba610.webp?t=1748186612\" width=592 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Running endlessly until you fail sounds weird. Well, you will run in this game from the horde of zombies, and if you make a mistake… You will fail and go again, nothing that bad. Try to beat the high score you or your friends set on all the maps available to you. If you get bored, you can try the hard mode with stamina that will keep you scrambling for donuts!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3/5 difficulty</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hard mode available</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards available</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/ba4cc779099c7137049c9704852fb764.poster.avif?t=1748186612\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/ba4cc779099c7137049c9704852fb764.webm?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/ba4cc779099c7137049c9704852fb764.mp4?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cabaret roulette</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/be279bfcc782aeaec2521526330ba610.webp?t=1748186612\" width=592 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A friendly game in a pub can never hurt unless you make this game about guns and the possibility of killing your enemy! Take turns shooting your opponent with a shotgun and use power-ups to enhance you or the current bullet in the weapon. Try to beat everyone and have your name listed as the ultimate Cabaret champion.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3/5 difficulty</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards available</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/1a847fac6927b100ec6af823ab99db5a.poster.avif?t=1748186612\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/1a847fac6927b100ec6af823ab99db5a.webm?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844310/extras/1a847fac6927b100ec6af823ab99db5a.mp4?t=1748186612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
